    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the Circadian Rhythms effects on the
      Norctrend Index in Anesthesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      It has been reported that circadian rhythm has many aspects of influence on human body. But
      little is knew about the circadian rhythm affect on Narcotrend index (made in Germany) in
      total intravenous anesthesia .The investigators' study is to find the relationship between
      them.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
